{"tid":2149781,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"恐怖分子頭目鄧炳強唔抵得被制裁，居然拖埋自己好兄弟落水！","createTime":"2020-08-10T14:51:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T14:59:43.000Z","uid":70786,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"da8cbd8753b5eacdb39d661da8df79c260dd3ea2","tid":2149781,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T14:51:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/5033752/org/8ad2cd91da804e31b23cd42074866379.jpg/EtZ7s2ZEtOXT5DWevs0dGvpDg1zpX877hMcKo4THCqM?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F5033752%2Forg%2F8ad2cd91da804e31b23cd42074866379.jpg%2FEtZ7s2ZEtOXT5DWevs0dGvpDg1zpX877hMcKo4THCqM%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=94c4f28f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強︰警隊試新招  「可信」媒體方准入封鎖線採訪<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fNeOMS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fNeOMS</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>警察公共關係科把關設名單<br />\n<br />\n何謂警方「信任」的媒體，鄧炳強指，要視乎媒體往績，有無作出一些警方認為並非專業記者所為的行為，包括是否持平報道、無參與報道以外活動、不會阻礙警方執行職務、不會對警務人員構成危險。至於批評警方的媒體，鄧炳強指「並無關係&hellip;歡迎任何人批評。」<br />\n<br />\n被問到是否變相警方對記者發牌，與篩選傳媒無異，鄧炳強皆否認，重申屬「行動決定」，涉及風險評估過程，視乎現場環境及案件場合決定，如謀殺案等的罪案交代照舊運作，警方其他記者會安排就如常跟從政府新聞處指引。主要在涉及公眾活動時試行該制度，由警察公共關係科（PPRB）與現場指揮官統籌，包括進入橙帶內的採訪活動空間、進入人數等。<br />\n<br />\n就搜查壹傳媒大樓的採訪安排，是否目前已設有「不信任名單」，及有關名單是否不可推翻抑或是浮動，鄧炳強未有透露，指不會評論個別機構，<span class=\"red\">僅表示PPRB會負責相關工作</span>。鄧炳強不同意該措拖是將傳媒分等級，不認同是「剝奪權利」及是「懲罰」，指是協助可信傳媒多些「著數」。就法律依據，他強調「這個是行動決定，正如橙帶要擺幾遠。」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cfwpdzz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCfwpdzz.png&h=950c31fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由鄧炳強出嚟認證，警方限制傳媒採訪，即係削弱緊香港新聞自由，任何削弱香港自由行為都可以被美國用香港人權法案制裁。既然採訪把關名單係由PPRB統籌，即係PPRB總警司郭嘉銓都會受到美國制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://tv.on.cc//xml/Thumbnail/202007/bigthumbnail/ONS200715-14833-01-M.jpg?t=1594741863\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftv.on.cc%2F%2Fxml%2FThumbnail%2F202007%2Fbigthumbnail%2FONS200715-14833-01-M.jpg%3Ft%3D1594741863&h=3681affa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n四十幾歲就俾人制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf1f5d6c9d281c64bef3df43a6b8c282b6a5299","tid":2149781,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T14:52:03.000Z","msg":"突發!肥佬黎上咗英國twitter trending!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fNfnRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fNfnRS</a>"},{"pid":"796cc47e786a84672b1f1dfd5ab15725b6561653","tid":2149781,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T14:52:58.000Z","msg":"[twitter要人］五眼聯盟聲明撐港，推到五眼加入制裁港共行列！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2147979\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2147979</a>"},{"pid":"a83d7cd07c8fabb4374e7316086f35efc5635268","tid":2149781,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T14:53:43.000Z","msg":"［上Twitter救蘋果］黎智英被捕震驚中外，大量外國議員/媒體報導。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2149128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2149128</a>"},{"pid":"aa20ad169de628624c8f65ae795c96f0fc154935","tid":2149781,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T14:56:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/japanavi/status/1292813875880943617\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjapanavi%2Fstatus%2F1292813875880943617&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mEYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=abda9088\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjapanavi%2Fstatus%2F1292813875880943617&h=977f7027\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/japanavi/status/1292813875880943617</a>"},{"pid":"b040fce2a9cb9c2beb0fece98f343ef09be3f24f","tid":2149781,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T14:57:24.000Z","msg":"推 已RT<br />\